		<!-------------- EXPERIENCE -------------->

			<section id="info-text">

				<h1 class="info">Hi, I’m Annie. I’m a designer and typographer designing editorial experiences. I’ve spent over 10 years as an in-house designer, primarily in the tech industry, working across brand and interactive teams.</h1>
				<p>I’m currently a Senior Designer at Mixpanel and have previously worked on design teams at <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/">Eventbrite</a>, <a href="https://www.wearesaatchi.com/">Saatchi & Saatchi</a>, <a href="https://www.everlane.com/">Everlane</a>, <a href="https://www.compass.com/">Compass</a>, and more. I’m known for my strong foundation in traditional graphic design and my love for typographic details, which I carry across print and web seamlessly.</p><br>
			<p>Typography is my happy place, so I am thrilled to be learning how to design typefaces this year through <a href="https://letterformarchive.org/type-west-online/">Type West</a>, a year-long type design and type history program through the <a href="https://letterformarchive.org/">Letterform Archive</a>—a dream! The program has brought me even closer to the web and makes me see type and my design practice in a new and inspiring way. I’m excited to see what comes next in my design journey, and welcome new design opportunities and collaborations!</p><br>
		
		</section>

		<section id="colophon">
			<h6>Colophon</h6>
			<p>This static website is designed and built by Annie Szafranski using <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> and GitHub pages—it is a work in progress. The logotype is set in <a href="https://lineto.com/typefaces/pirelli-vip">Pirelli</a> (A VIP) designed by Masahiro Nakamura and <a href="https://lineto.com/information/designers/lineto-designers/weichi-he">Weichi He</a>. The Headline copy is set in <a href="https://www.typemates.com/fonts/resonay">Resonay</a> by <a href="https://www.typemates.com/about/andrej-dienes">Andrej Dieneš</a>. The body copy is set in <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Spline+Sans">Spline Sans</a> by <a href="https://fonts.google.com/?query=Eben+Sorkin">Eben Sorkin</a> and <a href="https://fonts.google.com/?query=Mirko+Velimirovi%C4%87">Mirko Velimirović</a>.</p>
				
		</section>

